  "remarks": "\nAsdrubal José Brito Hernández is an involved person through his role as the Director of Criminal Investigations at the General Directorate of Military Counter-Intelligence (DGCIM). The DGCIM is and has been involved in the commission of serious human rights violations and abuses in Venezuela, including, but not limited to, “Operation Tun-Tun”, which followed the disputed July 2024 presidential election.\n",
